@node INSTALLATIONE "Installation"

@{b}Installation@{ub}

   Copy "WW-Print.rexx" in the drawer WWRexx. Then you go to "ARexx-Macro" in
   the Wordworth-menu "Extras", click on "new" and then on "WW-Print.rexx", of course.
   Now you can start it by another double-click.




@endnode
@node USEAGE "Useage"

   Start the program from Wordworth. You'll get a file requester for selecting one file.
   After that, you will be asked: "Print another file?" If you answer "no", printing
   will be started. If you answer "yes", you can select another file. (Sorry, multi-
   select isn't possible with WW)
   ATTENTION: There is a little @{"problem" link Problems} with the print settings!

@endnode
